{"tid":1925047,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"業主早知地基下沉  隔離酒店違建釀慘劇","createTime":"2020-03-14T05:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T06:09:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3e2679c6cb9eb556a2b75e5f1d2c07c73fe21de1","tid":1925047,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T05:57:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200314/YDJR3DVZ4CMICULRDFKSFEMYRU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200314%2FYDJR3DVZ4CMICULRDFKSFEMYRU%2F&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCUzY%2BUnkXQH0zW%2FJu7eEK44%3D&h=7c7b7822\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200314%2FYDJR3DVZ4CMICULRDFKSFEMYRU%2F&h=295b1a1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200314/YDJR3DVZ4CMICULRDFKSFEMYRU/</a><br />\n<br />\n業主早知地基下沉 <br />\n隔離酒店違建釀慘劇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200314/large/1584117970_c82a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200314%2Flarge%2F1584117970_c82a.gif&h=ddf70ab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n福建省泉州市隔離酒店倒塌（圖）造成29死慘劇，中國官方昨公佈初步調查結果，揭露涉事旅館工程未履行基本建設程序，無規劃和施工許可，存在非法建設、違規改造，以及屋主事先已知房屋地基下沉和承重柱變形等嚴重問題；批評地方部門監管不足，導致安全關卡層層失效，最終釀成慘劇。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：倫敦返港 16月大男嬰染疫<br />\n<br />\n29人罹難<br />\n<br />\n國務院「福建省泉州市欣佳酒店3&middot;7坍塌事故」調查組昨召開第一次全體會議，通報事故初步調查結果。初步調查結果指出，旅館工程未履行基本建設程序，無規劃和施工許可，存在非法建設、違規改造等嚴重問題，「特別是房屋業主發現房屋基礎沉降和承重柱變形等重大事故前兆，仍然心存僥偉 、繼續違規冒險經營」。調查結果亦提到，地方相關部門監管不足，「打非治違」流於形式。會議要求全面查清事故原因，以及涉事欣佳酒店違規經營和為何被選定醫學隔離觀察點以及有關政府部門失職、瀆職問題。被選定為醫學隔離觀察點的欣佳酒店上周六晚發生倒塌，造成29死42傷。<br />\n<br />\n中新社"},{"pid":"d79e7fb0ec168d58fc943a61ff9ca4dd31fa77cd","tid":1925047,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T05:58:32.000Z","msg":"中國製造"},{"pid":"a244e1a7c4182310705c657d8efcab0d436048fc","tid":1925047,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T06:04:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">符合<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>国</strong></span>情</span>"},{"pid":"8aa829a96d7b58ac7584f318242b9cd75dac13bb","tid":1925047,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T06:06:31.000Z","msg":"起好咁耐政府都發現唔到佢係違規起既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定係業主問題啦"},{"pid":"8441ea2deed60f551928cd93d12b2769817dd660","tid":1925047,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T06:09:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fSALQxA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfSALQxA.jpg&h=1aef1587&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}